snippet.title: Hoyle Casino Empire gameplay (PC Game, 2002)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Hoyle Casino Empire, PC game produced by Sierra in 2002 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/hoyle-casino-empire/10223/
Hoyle Casino Empire it is a management simulation game, manage your own gambling casino on the Las Vegas. The casino's level can be upgraded after meeting certain numbers of visitors and cashflow.
Played through modern Windows machine.
Recorded with original sound.
